      <title>可可价格上涨，因近期紧俏掩盖下一季作物盈余</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/cocoa-rises-as-near-term-tightness-overshadows-next-crop-surplus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管大宗商品经纪商 Marex Group 预测下一季可可产量将反弹，但由于供应紧张导致美国库存下降，纽约可可期货价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/cocoa-rises-as-near-term-tightness-overshadows-next-crop-surplus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:07:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦金属交易所暂停芬兰诺里尔斯克工厂的镍矿交付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/lme-to-suspend-deliveries-of-nickel-from-norilsk-finland-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所 (London Metal Exchange) 暂停俄罗斯 MMC Norilsk Nickel PJSC 旗下一家芬兰工厂的镍矿交付，尽管西方对俄罗斯金属实施制裁，但该公司的产品仍可交付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/lme-to-suspend-deliveries-of-nickel-from-norilsk-finland-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
