      <title>北约盟国同意为乌克兰提供 400 亿欧元资金目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/nato-allies-agree-on-40-billion-funding-target-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约外交官称，北约盟国周三同意，他们应每年向乌克兰提供至少 400 亿欧元（430 亿美元）的军事援助，但并未对未来几年做出明确承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/nato-allies-agree-on-40-billion-funding-target-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:41:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
